{"about_the_game":"Lwanda Magere was a nigh omnipotent being that once lived in Kenya (Africa). <br />\r\nThe Adventures of Lwanda Magere is a single-player action-adventure story based in Africa about his life experiences and interaction with other African heroes/beings. <br />\r\nGet to experience his life and abilities first hand: You take the role of Lwanda Magere who has supernatural abilities, you\u2019re immune to physical attacks but your shadow is the only weakness. You are the protector of the Luo people. You assist various communities and villages to maintain peace and order in any way possible. You\u2019re in certain missions assisted by your pets e.g. lion to accomplish certain tasks.<br />\r\nEnjoy the beautiful sights in Kenya and get to experience how powerful Lwanda Magere was as he settles disputes.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1658056539","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687780/page.bg.jpg?t=1658056539","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687780/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1658056539","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687780/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1658056539","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"The game contains half naked characters (both male and female) as it's a portrayal of the history of some African cultures attire and general dressing (in Kenyan tribes). There is violence (i.e. usage of spears, machete, animals attacking humans, there's also some little blood and skeletons)."},"detailed_description":"Lwanda Magere was a nigh omnipotent being that once lived in Kenya (Africa). <br />\r\nThe Adventures of Lwanda Magere is a single-player action-adventure story based in Africa about his life experiences and i